---
---

<section class="founder" aria-labelledby="founder-title">
  <div class="container inner reveal">
    <h2 class="sr-only" id="founder-title">Who runs Elliodelics</h2>
    <div class="founder-grid">
      <img
        class="portrait"
        src="/mike.webp"
        width="400"
        height="400"
        alt="Mike Elliott, smiling, with a yellow flower in his hair"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <div>
        <p class="lede">
          Elliodelics is <a class="mike" href="https://elliotec.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mike Elliott<span class="ext" aria-hidden="true">↗</span><span class="sr-only"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> — fifteen years building
          products and leading engineering organizations, now studying
          psychedelics and consciousness at the graduate level.
        </p>
        <p class="follow">
          Former Director of Engineering at Dutchie and ezCater. Founder of
          Mindscape Collective. MA candidate in Psychedelics &amp; Consciousness
          Studies at the University of Ottawa. He’s the person your CTO wants in
          the room, and the one your facilitators don’t mind having there.
        </p>
        <p class="aside mono">elliott × delics — the name was sitting right there</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder {
    background: var(--void);
    padding-block: var(--space-section);
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 58rem;
  }

  .founder-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 40rem) {
    .founder-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 9rem minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .portrait {
    width: 7.5rem;
    height: 7.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-faint);
  }
  @media (min-width: 40rem) {
    .portrait { width: 9rem; height: 9rem; }
  }

  .lede {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .mike {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--acid);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .mike:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .ext {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.45em;
    font-weight: 400;
    vertical-align: 0.9em;
    margin-inline-start: 0.3em;
  }

  .follow {
    max-width: var(--measure);
    margin: 1.8rem 0 0;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .aside {
    margin: 2.2rem 0 0;
    color: var(--acid);
  }
</style>
